Perfect! I have all the information you need. Let me provide a comprehensive overview of how app settings work in this Tauri app.

## Settings Architecture Overview

### 1. **Settings Data Model** (`src-tauri/src/config/mod.rs`, lines 163-191)

```rust
#[derive(Debug, Serialize, Deserialize, Clone, Default)]
pub struct AppSettings {
    pub anthropic_api_key: Option<String>,
    pub worktree_base_path: Option<String>,
}
```

The settings are stored as JSON at `~/.entire/app-settings.json`. Two key functions:

- **`read_app_settings()`** (lines 174-181): Reads from disk, returns default (empty) settings if file doesn't exist
- **`save_app_settings(settings: &AppSettings)`** (lines 183-191): Writes to `~/.entire/app-settings.json`, creating the `.entire` directory if needed

Both functions use `app_settings_path()` helper which constructs the path from the `HOME` environment variable.

### 2. **Settings UI** (`src/features/settings/SettingsView.tsx` - Full content below)

This is a modal dialog with two configurable fields:

**Field 1: Anthropic API key**
- Type: Password input (togglable visibility with Eye/EyeOff icons)
- Placeholder: `sk-ant-...`
- Help text: "Used for semantic review. Falls back to ANTHROPIC_API_KEY env var if empty."
- Stores in `AppSettings.anthropic_api_key`

**Field 2: Worktree base path**
- Type: Text input
- Placeholder: `/Users/me/Projects/wt`
- Help text: "Base directory for new worktrees. Leave empty to use repo-relative paths."
- Stores in `AppSettings.worktree_base_path`

The form:
- Fetches settings on mount via `useAppSettingsQuery()` hook
- Shows loading state while fetching
- Displays error messages from the mutation
- Shows "Saved" confirmation for 2 seconds on success
- Trims input values before saving (empty strings become `null`)

### 3. **Tauri Commands** (`src-tauri/src/lib.rs`, lines 75-82)

Two simple command handlers:

```rust
#[tauri::command]
fn get_app_settings() -> config::AppSettings {
    config::read_app_settings()
}

#[tauri::command]
fn save_app_settings(settings: config::AppSettings) -> Result<(), String> {
    config::save_app_settings(&settings)
}
```

Both are registered in the invoke handler (lines 874-875) for the frontend to call.

### 4. **Journal Directory** (`src-tauri/src/journal/mod.rs`, lines 52-58)

```rust
pub fn journal_dir() -> PathBuf {
    let home = std::env::var("HOME").unwrap_or_default();
    let dir = Path::new(&home).join(".entire/journal");
    let _ = fs::create_dir_all(&dir);
    dir
}
```

The journal system was recently changed to use **`~/.entire/journal/`** (the global user directory) instead of repo-relative paths. Journal entries are stored as markdown files named `YYYY-MM-DD.md` in this directory.

---

## Full SettingsView.tsx

```tsx
import { useState, useEffect, type FormEvent } from "react";
import { X, Eye, EyeOff } from "lucide-react";
import {
  useAppSettingsQuery,
  useSaveAppSettingsMutation,
  type AppSettings,
} from "../../hooks/use-tauri-query";

interface SettingsViewProps {
  onClose: () => void;
}

export function SettingsView({ onClose }: SettingsViewProps) {
  const { data: settings, isLoading } = useAppSettingsQuery();
  const saveMutation = useSaveAppSettingsMutation();
  const [apiKey, setApiKey] = useState("");
  const [worktreeBasePath, setWorktreeBasePath] = useState("");
  const [showApiKey, setShowApiKey] = useState(false);
  const [saved, setSaved] = useState(false);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (settings) {
      setApiKey(settings.anthropic_api_key ?? "");
      setWorktreeBasePath(settings.worktree_base_path ?? "");
    }
  }, [settings]);

  function handleSubmit(event: FormEvent<HTMLFormElement>) {
    event.preventDefault();
    const nextSettings: AppSettings = {
      anthropic_api_key: apiKey.trim() || null,
      worktree_base_path: worktreeBasePath.trim() || null,
    };
    saveMutation.mutate(nextSettings, {
      onSuccess: () => {
        setSaved(true);
        setTimeout(() => setSaved(false), 2000);
      },
    });
  }

  return (
    <div className="fixed inset-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 p-4">
      <form
        onSubmit={handleSubmit}
        className="w-full max-w-lg rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-overlay shadow-2xl"
      >
        <div className="flex items-center border-b border-border-subtle px-4 py-3">
          <div className="flex-1">
            <h3 className="text-sm font-semibold text-fg">Settings</h3>
            <p className="mt-0.5 text-xs text-fg-muted">App configuration</p>
          </div>
          <button
            type="button"
            onClick={onClose}
            className="flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded text-fg-subtle transition-colors hover:bg-bg-hover hover:text-fg"
            title="Close settings"
          >
            <X size={14} />
          </button>
        </div>

        {isLoading ? (
          <div className="px-4 py-8 text-center text-xs text-fg-subtle">
            Loading settings...
          </div>
        ) : (
          <div className="space-y-5 px-4 py-4">
            <label className="block text-xs text-fg-muted">
              Anthropic API key
              <p className="mb-1 text-[11px] text-fg-subtle">
                Used for semantic review. Falls back to ANTHROPIC_API_KEY env var if empty.
              </p>
              <div className="relative">
                <input
                  type={showApiKey ? "text" : "password"}
                  value={apiKey}
                  onChange={(e) => setApiKey(e.target.value)}
                  placeholder="sk-ant-..."
                  autoComplete="off"
                  autoCorrect="off"
                  autoCapitalize="off"
                  spellCheck={false}
                  className="mt-1 w-full rounded border border-border bg-bg-raised px-3 py-2 pr-9 text-sm text-fg outline-none transition-colors placeholder:text-fg-subtle focus:border-accent"
                />
                <button
                  type="button"
                  onClick={() => setShowApiKey(!showApiKey)}
                  className="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-fg-subtle hover:text-fg"
                  tabIndex={-1}
                >
                  {showApiKey ? <EyeOff size={14} /> : <Eye size={14} />}
                </button>
              </div>
            </label>

            <label className="block text-xs text-fg-muted">
              Worktree base path
              <p className="mb-1 text-[11px] text-fg-subtle">
                Base directory for new worktrees. Leave empty to use repo-relative paths.
              </p>
              <input
                value={worktreeBasePath}
                onChange={(e) => setWorktreeBasePath(e.target.value)}
                placeholder="/Users/me/Projects/wt"
                autoComplete="off"
                autoCorrect="off"
                autoCapitalize="off"
                spellCheck={false}
                className="mt-1 w-full rounded border border-border bg-bg-raised px-3 py-2 text-sm text-fg outline-none transition-colors placeholder:text-fg-subtle focus:border-accent"
              />
            </label>

            {saveMutation.error && (
              <div className="rounded bg-red-bg px-3 py-2 text-xs text-red">
                {saveMutation.error.message}
              </div>
            )}
          </div>
        )}

        <div className="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-border-subtle px-4 py-3">
          {saved && (
            <span className="text-xs text-green">Saved</span>
          )}
          <button
            type="button"
            onClick={onClose}
            className="rounded border border-border px-3 py-2 text-xs text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:border-border-hover hover:text-fg"
          >
            Cancel
          </button>
          <button
            type="submit"
            disabled={saveMutation.isPending}
            className="rounded bg-accent px-3 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-60"
          >
            {saveMutation.isPending ? "Saving..." : "Save"}
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  );
}
```

---

## Key Technical Details

- **Storage format**: JSON at `~/.entire/app-settings.json`
- **API fallback**: The Anthropic API key can fall back to the `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` environment variable if the settings field is empty
- **Worktree handling**: The `worktree_base_path` setting is used by the worktree creation logic (in `src-tauri/src/git/mod.rs`) to determine where new worktrees are created
- **Journal storage**: Recently unified to use `~/.entire/journal/` (not repo-relative), with markdown files for each date
- **UI pattern**: Modal dialog with form submission, loading state, error display, and success confirmation

